item.title: Thank you
item.description:
Thank you 

for taking the time to check out our Alfa. As you see, it is in great condition, it starts, runs and looks pretty much as it did when purchased by the original owner. I am the second owner, since 1987. It has been garaged all of it's life. (Click the pics to see full size and original color.)
